@koher futureMapだと元々のMapの機能とか失っちゃってかなり勿体無いので
```swift
protocol FutureLike {
    associatedtype Output
    associatedtype Failure: Error

    func asFuture() -> Future<Output, Failure>
}
```
こういうの作って
```swift
extension Publishers.Map: FutureLike where Upstream: FutureLike {
    func asFuture() -> Future<Output, Upstream.Failure> {
        Future(self)
    }
}
```
こうした方が良いですね

